Yuzo Koshiro is a BGM god.

Goddamn, the EO games have such awesome music... and this doesn't help keep them from being awesome at all.

Cherry Tree Bridge was particularly awesome in the first place though.  Even if the game was menacing as heck by that point, it actually made me stop and just admire the beauty of the area for a while... something you wouldn't expect from a system of the DS' power.
